{"tid":690673,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"珍妮花將任《老友記》好姊妹歌翠妮伴娘","createTime":"2018-06-05T05:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T15:58:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df1f909834b5a8be6fe8fb650a156747e278d26f","tid":690673,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"49歲荷李活女星珍妮花雅麗絲頓（Jennifer Aniston）同歌翠妮葛絲（Courteney Cox），因經典美劇《老友記》（Friends）而成為好姊妹，經歷離婚時又陪伴對方左右。最近歌翠妮葛絲將會再婚，下嫁歌手Johnny McDaid，而珍妮花亦會擔任其伴娘！<br />\n<br />\n最近再次經歷離婚傷痛嘅珍妮花，噚日同好姊妹歌翠妮結伴出席品牌活動，相中見到珍妮花整親隻手，不過佢都刻意收埋。消息人士指：「如果唔係珍妮花陪佢，歌翠妮就唔想行入教堂。佢哋嘅友情非常堅定。」而於2015年珍妮花嫁第二任老公Justin Theroux時，歌翠妮都係對方伴娘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/131323_7a26c95534c360fbf297c0552ec434d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F131323_7a26c95534c360fbf297c0552ec434d6.png&h=3e11f9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180604/58277176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58277176&d=lY5kZ2wbYh2qA7mbLejyKrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c995021a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58277176&h=5bdcbd79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180604/58277176</a>"},{"pid":"307fa9fd004208eaa36e3faf98e77da3face3123","tid":690673,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24fabdb79c9babbf8c9085590b968ce0b5915141","tid":690673,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"變晒樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c9e6f058945410ea8bed984b1644627b04339f","tid":690673,"uid":27324